{
  "id": "RAW_f06343cb",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-16）：快手可灵与港科大联合推出 UnityVideo，统一多模态视频理解框架，重塑视频生成与感知新范式",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500917&idx=1&sn=0c314938a6e5298f7342e90333296bfb",
  "date": "2025-12-16 09:44:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：UnityVideo</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"784\" data-imgfileid=\"100017255\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe62409b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPe74iaEOpfRgyCug9ZhaDLSHyUCDpVeQuLBxicKRlupfu41RInTWlag58A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UnityVideo是一个统一的多模态多任务视频理解框架，旨在增强对世界的感知能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目支持从</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">文本</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">生成</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高质量视频</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并提供对视频生成的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">细粒度控制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。它能够从视频中估计</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度、法线</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">等多种模态，并在无需额外训练的情况下对新对象和风格表现出强大的泛化能力。其统一架构在多个视频生成基准上实现了最先进的性能，同时保持了效率和可扩展性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unityvideo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unityvideo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Trust-videoLLMs</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"404\" data-imgfileid=\"100017254\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f94cc10&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPeAqsyI9NnLzkasMoYJeGWsVKkpx0PFwpXNls18hhT8goqB1Lmk1WyWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Trust-videoLLMs 是一个强大的基准测试工具，旨在评估视频大语言模型（videoLLMs）在五个关键维度上的表现：真实性、安全性、鲁棒性、公平性和隐私性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目涵盖了30个任务，涉及改编、合成和注释视频，以评估动态视觉场景、跨模态交互和现实世界的安全性考虑。对23个最先进的视频LLMs（5个商业模型，18个开源模型）的评估显示，在动态视觉场景理解和跨模态扰动的适应性方面存在显著局限性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trust-videollms\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/trust-videollms</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Chatterbox-Turbo</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"404\" data-imgfileid=\"100017252\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=968f690d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPer33RZF0Bsy5qGOOMdXlmWafV3omRy9iaF2cAzibOR8weaIhnVCWXXnqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Chatterbox-Turbo是Resemble AI推出的最新高效文本转语音模型。该模型基于350M参数架构，能够在较低的计算和显存需求下生成高质量的语音。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过简化语音令牌到梅尔频谱的解码过程，生成步骤从10步减少到1步，同时保持高保真音频输出。Turbo模型原生支持副语言标记，如[cough]、[laugh]等，增强了语音的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">真实感</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该模型主要用于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">低延迟语音Agent</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，但在旁白和创意工作流中也表现出色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/chatterbox-turbo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/chatterbox-turbo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：CCD-DLM-code&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6064814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"706\" data-imgfileid=\"100017253\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eefa8b9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPeRx5q1ibbugz7icyzG4FhVRqiaQynJkdTUQE6JheibNf44ibDnHv1bFKQHaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CCD-DLM-code 是一个用于扩散语言模型（DLMs）的新颖解码方法的官方代码。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了一种从新视角出发的解码方法，旨在提高解码的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自适应性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">连贯性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。项目目前提供了一个初步的 PyTorch 实现，并计划在未来提供完整的代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ccd-dlm-code\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ccd-dlm-code</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MU</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36018518518518516\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"420\" data-imgfileid=\"100017251\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a2c63b3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPeUmuanHGAfQN62cCPZDFd07Rt7fMibJicZ1jHmHqRG0miaduJV9mQ4ibYRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MU 是一个用于理解代码库的工具，它通过将代码库解析为语义图数据库，实现快速查询、语义搜索和差异分析。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">MU 可以在几秒钟内将整个代码库提供给 AI，而不是几个小时。它能够压缩代码库以便于 LLM（大语言模型）处理，并提供结构化的压缩和语义搜索功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mu-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mu-2</a> &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：EfficientFlow</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"488\" data-imgfileid=\"100017256\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3affbdc6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw93qjkpb7jicRhqAoHobXPeMgNR6KkOcWksyeDCuANAm1dSFuKbEQwCVM8hZwBKQTibIhXIdYZIM7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EfficientFlow是一个面向具身人工智能的高效等变流策略学习项目，该项目旨在通过等变性流策略来提升机器人在复杂环境中的学习效率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目提供了完整的训练和评估流程，支持使用MimicGen数据集进行训练，并提供了数据集转换工具以适应不同的动作空间需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/efficientflow\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/efficientflow</a></span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "今日开源（2025-12-16）：快手可灵与港科大联合推出 UnityVideo，统一多模态视频理解框架，重塑视频生成与感知新范式，同时还介绍了其他五项 AI 领域的最新开源项目进展。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "今日开源（2025-12-16）：快手可灵与港科大联合推出 UnityVideo，统一多模态视频理解框架，重塑视频生成与感知新范式，同时还介绍了其他五项 AI 领域的最新开源项目进展。",
  "summary": "文章《今日开源》集中发布了 2025 年 12 月 16 日最新开源的六个 AI 项目。其中包括：快手可灵与港科大联合推出的多模态视频理解框架 UnityVideo，它能实现高质量视频生成和深度/法线估计；评估视频大语言模型性能的基准测试工具 Trust-videoLLMs；Resemble AI 的高效文本转语音模型 Chatterbox-Turbo，显著降低语音生成延迟；扩散语言模型的新型解码方法 CCD-DLM-code；用于将代码库解析为语义图数据库以供 LLM 快速处理的工具 MU；以及提升机器人在复杂环境中学习效率的具身人工智能项目 EfficientFlow。整体内容为短新闻式汇总，每个项目介绍简明扼要，并提供了收藏链接。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
